Performs authentication services in the jaas environment. caArray needs both CSM authentication, using the CSM tables with encrypted passwords, and the JBoss password stacking mechanism to be able to authenticate via LDAP but get role information from CSM. This class bridges between the CSM world and JBoss.
Delegates to the superclass and, if successful, adds options for JBoss password stacking. {@inheritDoc}
